# Set Features

This directory contains Gherkin feature files for Set interface examples.

## Planned Features

- HashSet (uniqueness, hashCode)
- LinkedHashSet (insertion order preservation)
- TreeSet (natural ordering, Comparator)

## Structure

Each feature file should follow the pattern:
```
# language: es

Característica: [Feature description]
  Como desarrollador Java
  Quiero [objective]
  Para [benefit]

  Escenario: [Scenario description]
    Dado [precondition]
    Cuando [action]
    Entonces [expected result]
```

## Notes

- All features should be written in neutral Spanish
- Focus on demonstrating uniqueness behavior
- Include scenarios showing differences between Set implementations
- Explain hashCode/equals contract for HashSet
